<p>Good day,</p>

<p>@ApplicationParameters?.EmployeeName has submitted a request to apply for @ApplicationParameters?.TrainingType language training with the NRCan Language School. </p>
<p>As the manager, your approval is required before the request is submitted to the Language School for consideration. Please note that by approving this request, it does not guarantee that training will be available for your employee. Language training offerings are based on demand and availability of the teachers. Courses will only be offered if there is sufficient demand to fill a class (minimum 4 students).      </p>

<p><u>Please review your employee information via the following link:</u></p>
<p><a href=@ApplicationParameters?.AppUrl >@ApplicationParameters?.AppUrl</a></p>


<p><b>New users:</b></p>
<p>1.	You will be asked to choose an account – choose your NRCan e-mail address</p>
<p>2.	Select language</p>
<p>3.	Read and accept Terms and Conditions and click submit</p>
<p><b>All other users:</b></p>
<p>1.	Click ‘Tools’ (on the left of the window).</p>
<p>2.	On the Tools page, locate the Language Training Webform and click ‘Open’.</p>
<p>3.	Click ‘Pending’ (next to the requested language training). The form will open at the bottom of the page.</p>
<p>4.	Once you have selected the appropriate ‘Manager Decision’ at the end of the form, click ‘Submit’.</p>


